# Badge — React

Package: `@acko/badge`
Directive: None (presentational)

## Props Interface

```typescript
type BadgeTextCase = 'uppercase' | 'title' | 'sentence';

interface BadgeProps {
  variant?: 'solid' | 'outline' | 'dot';
  color?: 'purple' | 'green' | 'blue' | 'orange' | 'pink' | 'gray';
  size?: 'sm' | 'md' | 'lg';
  textCase?: BadgeTextCase;  // default: 'uppercase' — no lowercase in badges
  removable?: boolean;
  onRemove?: () => void;
  className?: string;
  children: ReactNode;
}

interface CounterBadgeProps {
  count: number;
  max?: number;
  color?: 'purple' | 'pink' | 'blue';
  className?: string;
}
```

## Component Pattern

Zero Tailwind utilities. Pure `clsx` class composition:
- `acko-badge`, `acko-badge-{size}`, `acko-badge-{variant}-{color}`, text case class

Text case mapping:
- `uppercase` → `acko-badge-uppercase` (default)
- `title` → `acko-badge-title-case`
- `sentence` → `acko-badge-sentence-case`

